b'Licca-chan to Yamaneko Hoshi no Tabi':
b'Based on the popular Licca doll in Japan. Licca meets a mysterious cat.

Licca goes on vacation with her father. The town in the mountains they go to is the site of a festival of the stars that has a mystical background, which is more real than Licca expected when she ends up in the middle of the mystical battle for the festival.

(Source: AniDB)'
[b'Super Doll Licca-chan', b'Licca-chan Fushigi na Mahou no Ring', b'Licca-chan no Nichiyoubi', b'Licca-chan Fushigi na Fushigi na Yunia Monogatari']
